  <name>VGP Monitor</name>
  <summary>F-16 engine-page style system monitor</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Real-time system monitor rendered as an F-16 engine instrument page.
      CPU / MEM / GPU / SWAP shown as tape-scale gauges with caret pointer
      and bracketed digital readout. Per-core utilization as a bracketed
      readout grid.
    </p>
  </description>
